{"parentUuid":"ed62485f-8090-4bed-9859-4d86c0fec6d1","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_012jd88Qvu2vpWhSwLQuVQSF","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Much cleaner. The outer loop is now just:\n\n```python\nfor lock_entity_id in lock_entity_ids:\n    try:\n        lock_instance, unmanaged = await _query_lock(lock_entity_id)\n    except LockCodeManagerError:\n        continue\n    except Exception:\n        _LOGGER.warning(...)\n        continue\n    if unmanaged:\n        result[lock_entity_id] = unmanaged\n        lock_instances[lock_entity_id] = lock_instance\n```\n\nAll the validation/logging lives in `_query_lock` which raises `LockCodeManagerError` for expected skips and lets unexpected exceptions propagate."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":631,"cache_read_input_tokens":402163,"output_tokens":159,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":631,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CZjeNuidVsPvCStnNRjbT","type":"assistant","uuid":"2b5be9d9-b2ad-4d87-9a33-835e3e78a09e","timestamp":"2026-04-05T00:03:53.203Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/raman/projects/lock_code_manager","sessionId":"3f097ff1-5bb6-4622-8cfe-35782dd270ba","version":"2.1.81","gitBranch":"feat/lock-reset-step","slug":"jolly-wandering-moonbeam"}
