{"parentUuid":"fd94388e-0e6d-449c-82a7-531f8e9b3f08","isSidechain":false,"promptId":"3a019ed9-46fa-47ed-8090-7c06a51eca95","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"yes do 1, how would you address 2?"},"uuid":"a8a5eda2-2be8-4fbc-8631-4cbfafd93a4b","timestamp":"2026-04-05T00:16:14.207Z","permissionMode":"bypassPermissions","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/raman/projects/lock_code_manager","sessionId":"3f097ff1-5bb6-4622-8cfe-35782dd270ba","version":"2.1.81","gitBranch":"feat/lock-reset-step","slug":"jolly-wandering-moonbeam"}
{"parentUuid":"a8a5eda2-2be8-4fbc-8631-4cbfafd93a4b","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01BZDVTJswC7vwh3DZDnuB6d","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nFor #2, the pattern is:\n\n```python\nfor lock_entity_id, codes in self._unmanaged_codes.items():\n    lock_instance = self._lock_instances.get(lock_entity_id)\n    if not lock_instance:\n        _LOGGER.warning(...)\n        continue\n    for slot in <some_slots>:\n        try:\n            await lock_instance.async_internal_clear_usercode(slot, source=\"direct\")\n        except Exception:\n            _LOGGER.warning(\"Failed to clear slot %s on %s\", slot, lock_entity_id, ...)\n```\n\nThis appears in `async_step_lock_reset_clear` (all slots) and `async_step_lock_reset_adopt` (masked slots only). The only difference is which slots to clear.\n\nA helper method on the flow class:\n\n```python\nasync def _clear_slots(\n    self, slots_to_clear: dict[str, list[int]]\n) -> None:\n    \"\"\"Clear specified slots on each lock, logging failures.\"\"\"\n    for lock_entity_id, slots in slots_to_clear.items():\n        lock_instance = self._lock_instances.get(lock_entity_id)\n        if not lock_instance:\n            _LOGGER.warning(\n                \"No lock instance for %s; cannot clear codes\",\n                lock_entity_id,\n            )\n            continue\n        for slot in slots:\n            try:\n                await lock_instance.async_internal_clear_usercode(\n                    slot, source=\"direct\"\n                )\n            except Exception:  # noqa: BLE001\n                _LOGGER.warning(\n                    \"Failed to clear slot %s on %s\",\n                    slot, lock_entity_id, exc_info=True,\n                )\n```\n\nThen the callers become:\n\n```python\n# Clear step: clear all unmanaged slots\nawait self._clear_slots({\n    lock_id: list(codes) for lock_id, codes in self._unmanaged_codes.items()\n})\n\n# Adopt step: clear only masked slots\nawait self._clear_slots({\n    lock_id: [s for s, c in codes.items() if c is SlotCode.UNKNOWN]\n    for lock_id, codes in self._unmanaged_codes.items()\n})\n```\n\nWant me to do both in the same PR or separate?"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":272,"cache_read_input_tokens":422221,"output_tokens":567,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":272,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CZjfLM6eHDhQ7nJgJuXUS","type":"assistant","uuid":"afcfdfca-e4ce-4c98-9d0c-740213dc1b6d","timestamp":"2026-04-05T00:16:30.908Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/raman/projects/lock_code_manager","sessionId":"3f097ff1-5bb6-4622-8cfe-35782dd270ba","version":"2.1.81","gitBranch":"feat/lock-reset-step","slug":"jolly-wandering-moonbeam"}
