{"parentUuid":"50cc53d5-5d49-4aaf-a741-3e6b4390febd","isSidechain":false,"promptId":"4e40bf0b-dda0-407c-b4ce-ad307e81110d","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_019gk1hib4r4XuzHZEBx5Z9T","type":"tool_result","content":"/Users/raman/.claude/shell-snapshots/snapshot-bash-1775143734045-fw9p9j.sh: line 372: alias: --: not found\n{\"author\":\"jprasm\",\"body\":\"I really apprecaite you helping me here!\\n\\n1. Matter integration shows both U200 locks:\\n\\n\\u003cimg width=\\\"1035\\\" height=\\\"525\\\" alt=\\\"Image\\\" src=\\\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/89cc8a68-f8b3-4d4a-9707-e9ee513ada08\\\" /\\u003e\\n\\n2. I'm using HA version 2026.4.1\\n\\nHere is a sample of the logs (let me know if you need more)....there are indeed some errors here.\\n\\n**I'm seeing a lot of this:**\\n\\n2026-04-04 10:29:05.722 DEBUG (MainThread) [custom_components.lock_code_manager.providers] Lock lock.door_to_garage: push subscription deferred: Matter client or node ID unavailable for lock.door_to_garage\\n2026-04-0\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-04T14:46:03Z\"}\n{\"author\":\"raman325\",\"body\":\"Thanks for the logs! Two issues visible:\\n\\n**1. Push subscription failing (\\\"Matter client or node ID unavailable\\\")**\\n\\nThis is why the event entity is greyed out. The lock provider can't find the Matter client or resolve the node ID from the device registry. Can you check:\\n\\n1. In Developer Tools → States, search for `lock.door_to_garage` — does it show a `device_id` in the attributes?\\n2. In Developer Tools → Template, paste this and share the result:\\n```jinja\\n{% set lock = states.lock.door_to_garage %}\\ndevice_id: {{ lock.attributes.get('device_id', 'NOT SET') }}\\nentity_id: {{ lock.entity_id }}\\n`\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-05T04:21:52Z\"}\n{\"author\":\"jprasm\",\"body\":\"Good morning! Here are some answers for you:\\n\\n**1. Push subscription failing (\\\"Matter client or node ID unavailable\\\")**\\n\\n1. There is no device_id in the attributes for lock.door_to_garage or lock.cold_storage_room (both aqara U200 locks, the only locks I have by the way). \\n\\n\\u003cimg width=\\\"2280\\\" height=\\\"348\\\" alt=\\\"Image\\\" src=\\\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/8ae3d4b2-5166-499a-8557-0dc5ade6fbcb\\\" /\\u003e\\n\\n2. Template result is: device_id: NOT SET ; entity_id: lock.door_to_garage\\n\\n\\u003cimg width=\\\"2288\\\" height=\\\"307\\\" alt=\\\"Image\\\" src=\\\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/aa1d143b-8530-47eb-88aa-4\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-05T11:14:00Z\"}","is_error":false}]},"uuid":"15ba04fc-b662-4c2c-944e-7c7ef07297ca","timestamp":"2026-04-05T13:02:46.027Z","toolUseResult":{"stdout":"/Users/raman/.claude/shell-snapshots/snapshot-bash-1775143734045-fw9p9j.sh: line 372: alias: --: not found\n{\"author\":\"jprasm\",\"body\":\"I really apprecaite you helping me here!\\n\\n1. Matter integration shows both U200 locks:\\n\\n\\u003cimg width=\\\"1035\\\" height=\\\"525\\\" alt=\\\"Image\\\" src=\\\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/89cc8a68-f8b3-4d4a-9707-e9ee513ada08\\\" /\\u003e\\n\\n2. I'm using HA version 2026.4.1\\n\\nHere is a sample of the logs (let me know if you need more)....there are indeed some errors here.\\n\\n**I'm seeing a lot of this:**\\n\\n2026-04-04 10:29:05.722 DEBUG (MainThread) [custom_components.lock_code_manager.providers] Lock lock.door_to_garage: push subscription deferred: Matter client or node ID unavailable for lock.door_to_garage\\n2026-04-0\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-04T14:46:03Z\"}\n{\"author\":\"raman325\",\"body\":\"Thanks for the logs! Two issues visible:\\n\\n**1. Push subscription failing (\\\"Matter client or node ID unavailable\\\")**\\n\\nThis is why the event entity is greyed out. The lock provider can't find the Matter client or resolve the node ID from the device registry. Can you check:\\n\\n1. In Developer Tools → States, search for `lock.door_to_garage` — does it show a `device_id` in the attributes?\\n2. In Developer Tools → Template, paste this and share the result:\\n```jinja\\n{% set lock = states.lock.door_to_garage %}\\ndevice_id: {{ lock.attributes.get('device_id', 'NOT SET') }}\\nentity_id: {{ lock.entity_id }}\\n`\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-05T04:21:52Z\"}\n{\"author\":\"jprasm\",\"body\":\"Good morning! Here are some answers for you:\\n\\n**1. Push subscription failing (\\\"Matter client or node ID unavailable\\\")**\\n\\n1. There is no device_id in the attributes for lock.door_to_garage or lock.cold_storage_room (both aqara U200 locks, the only locks I have by the way). \\n\\n\\u003cimg width=\\\"2280\\\" height=\\\"348\\\" alt=\\\"Image\\\" src=\\\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/8ae3d4b2-5166-499a-8557-0dc5ade6fbcb\\\" /\\u003e\\n\\n2. Template result is: device_id: NOT SET ; entity_id: lock.door_to_garage\\n\\n\\u003cimg width=\\\"2288\\\" height=\\\"307\\\" alt=\\\"Image\\\" src=\\\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/aa1d143b-8530-47eb-88aa-4\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-05T11:14:00Z\"}","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false},"sourceToolAssistantUUID":"50cc53d5-5d49-4aaf-a741-3e6b4390febd","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/raman/projects/lock_code_manager","sessionId":"3f097ff1-5bb6-4622-8cfe-35782dd270ba","version":"2.1.81","gitBranch":"feat/lock-reset-step","slug":"jolly-wandering-moonbeam"}
