{"parentUuid":"3aa1ee34-8cce-4440-8ca2-7afbae3b13ba","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_013Pnsxza6Ev4cieVJsX4tUb","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01EPpkW3VM1tt5BqdiPPckQM","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"gh pr create --title \"Warn when lock entity has no device ID\" --body \"$(cat <<'EOF'\n## Proposed change\n\nLog a warning in `BaseLock.__post_init__` when the lock entity is missing a `device_id`. Without a device ID, features like Matter event subscriptions and device-based identification are unavailable.\n\nHelps diagnose issues like #984 where the Matter integration didn't link the lock entity to its device, causing silent failures in push subscriptions and event tracking.\n\n## Type of change\n\n- [ ] Dependency upgrade\n- [x] Bugfix (non-breaking change which fixes an issue)\n- [ ] New feature (which adds functionality)\n- [ ] Breaking change (fix/feature causing existing functionality to break)\n- [ ] Code quality improvements to existing code or addition of tests\n\n## Additional information\n\n- This PR is related to issue: #984\n- 550 tests pass, all pre-commit hooks pass\n\n🤖 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)\nEOF\n)\" 2>&1","description":"Create PR"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":744,"cache_read_input_tokens":476160,"output_tokens":310,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":744,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CZkg8NtLWAst7HL5SsYNH","type":"assistant","uuid":"ca129406-5dad-4ca4-8311-8d47aef28cf6","timestamp":"2026-04-05T13:07:27.863Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/raman/projects/lock_code_manager","sessionId":"3f097ff1-5bb6-4622-8cfe-