{"parentUuid":"ccf3d667-fd15-4ea1-9240-82cdfe117f81","isSidechain":false,"promptId":"fadfe915-fe93-43c0-a717-92147286b7c7","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"ok I think things are working now, it's just a timeout issue. I will try moving closer to the antenna. It's a Eufy E31 btw"},"uuid":"17264702-522c-4663-be03-bb1523b55df1","timestamp":"2026-04-06T21:00:51.780Z","permissionMode":"bypassPermissions","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/raman/projects/lock_code_manager","sessionId":"3f097ff1-5bb6-4622-8cfe-35782dd270ba","version":"2.1.81","gitBranch":"main","slug":"jolly-wandering-moonbeam"}
{"parentUuid":"17264702-522c-4663-be03-bb1523b55df1","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01L6veL2VygcY96569nXH7DA","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nEufy E31 — good choice for testing. That's one of the more popular Matter locks and supports the User Management cluster we need.\n\nYeah, commissioning timeout is usually a proximity issue. The lock needs to reach the border router during the initial join even though Thread is mesh-routed afterwards. A few feet away is usually enough.\n\nA couple things specific to the Eufy E31 once you get past commissioning:\n\n1. **Initial PIN setup** — the Eufy might come with a default admin PIN already configured. After commissioning, check if `get_lock_users` returns any existing credentials. If there are codes set from before, the lock reset step (PR #983) will offer to clear them.\n\n2. **PIN length** — the Eufy E31 supports 4-8 digit PINs. Make sure your test PINs are within that range.\n\n3. **PIN uniqueness** — based on issue #984, Aqara enforces unique PINs across slots. The Eufy may or may not — worth testing by trying to set the same PIN on two slots and seeing if it returns \"duplicate\".\n\n4. **Event tracking** — once commissioned, try using a PIN at the keypad. The LockOperation event should fire and you should see the event entity update with `pin_used`.\n\nLet me know when commissioning succeeds and we'll go through LCM setup."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":958,"cache_read_input_tokens":661770,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":958},"output_tokens":4,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"}},"requestId":"req_011CZoC44c8jNwiMDhc41dZM","type":"assistant","uuid":"0e688bc1-e3fb-4f35-a494-7fac7b134511","timestamp":"2026-04-06T21:01:06.503Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/raman/projects/lock_code_manager","sessionId":"3f097ff1-5bb6-4622-8cfe-35782dd270ba","version":"2.1.81","gitBranch":"main","slug":"jolly-wandering-moonbeam"}
